ivating the sense that whatever good work you are doing is being done by th=
e Lord *through you* and whatever results (including very bad ones) are giv=
en to you are fruits granted by the Lord to your karmas which you should ac=
cept without regrets, is an important activity that should go on outside of=
 the ritual time.
 
